WebGL,is,a,web,standard,for,APIs,that,allow,users,to,work,with,low,level,D,graphics,in,a,browser,without,the,need,for,a,plugin,The,standard,is,based,on,OpenGL,ES,and,stays,very,close,to,that,specification,The,WebGL,standard,functions,across,platforms,and,is,provided,royalty,free,The,vendors,for,the,Safari,Chrome,Firefox,and,Opera,browsers,are,members,of,the,WebGL,Working,Group